# Keep test files out of the deployment. Vitest runs them in CI / locally, never
# at build time. Critically, any `api/*.test.ts` would otherwise be treated as a
# Serverless Function — and that pushed a deployment to 14 functions, over the
# Hobby plan's cap of 12 per deployment. (Helper-style `api/_*.test.ts` are
# already ignored by Vercel's `_`-prefix rule; the route-level test files are
# not, which is what this covers.)
**/*.test.ts
**/*.test.tsx
**/*.spec.ts
**/*.spec.tsx
